## About Me

I am a Salesforce Developer passionate about building innovative solutions that drive business success. With experience in Apex, Visualforce, and Lightning, I enjoy collaborating with cross-functional teams to deliver high-quality applications.

## Technologies Used

- Salesforce Apex
- Visualforce
- Lightning Web Components (LWC)
- Git & GitHub
- REST/SOAP APIs

## Projects

### Project 1: [Kaseya]
**Description**:
  
            . Kaseya provides cloud-based IT management and security software that enables IT organizations
              and Debook Rebook Tool to automatically cancel multiple subscriptions.
  **Key activities performed**:
  
            . Analyzing requirements and Involving in the development of modules.
            . Involved in debugging, troubleshooting, and taking responsibility to see that the issue is fully resolved.
            . Worked on various Salesforce CPQ requirements.
            . Involved in setting products, bundles and products and pricing rules.
            . Implemented out of box configuration of discounting, pricing methods and output document generation.
            . Implemented advanced approvals in salesforce to simplify approval process for Sales Ops.
            . Implemented Web Service Callouts from Salesforce to external applications using REST API.
            . Created connected apps for integration.
            . Worked on JIRA tool for tracking the enhancements and developments, managed and coordinated with offshore team
              and got the user stories delivered to the client on time within the sprints.
            . Gathered user requirements and was involved in application design discussions and documentation.
            . Proactively identified areas of improvement and functional gaps in Salesforce Applications
            . Worked on document generation with merge fields using Conga.
            . Worked on advance formula fields creation.
            . Worked on the designing of custom objects, custom fields, page layouts, custom Tabs, custom reports, report folders,
              design of Visual Force Pages, Dashboards and various other components as per the client and application requirements.
            . Used SOQL in Apex Triggers, Controllers and Database methods for performing DML operations.
            . Created Test classes for unit testing of the apex classes.
            . Created roles, profiles and implemented security and sharing rules at object, field, and record level for different users at
              different levels of the organization.
            . Implemented the approval process and workflow rules to automate existing business processes.
            . Implemented pick lists, dependent pick lists, lookups, master-detail relationships, validation and formula fields to the
              custom objects.
            . Created and maintained reports and dashboards to provide fast access to key business metrics.
            . Prepared Technical Design Documents and deployment plans as per user stories and bugs.
  
**Technologies**:

  Tools: Data Loader, Workbench, Force.com platform, Visual Studio Code.
  
  Technologies: Salesforce
  
  Skills: Salesforce CRM, Salesforce Lightning Experience, Visualforce Pages, Apex Classes, Apex Triggers, Flows, JavaScript.


